Before modifying key: Value1
After modifying key: null
Best Practices
âœ… Use immutable objects as HashMap keys (e.g., String, Integer).
âœ… If using a custom object as a key, make its fields immutable (final).
âœ… Do not modify key attributes that affect hashCode() and equals().

